# Chess App Design System

## Theme: Dark

The app uses a **unified dark theme**. Never introduce light backgrounds, white cards, or colorful page gradients.

## Color Tokens

```scss
$bg:      #0d0d14;   // page background
$bg2:     #161622;   // card / surface
$bg3:     #1e1e2e;   // elevated element inside card
$border:  rgba(255,255,255,.07);   // subtle border
$border2: rgba(255,255,255,.12);   // hover border
$accent:  #7c6af7;   // primary action color
$accent-l:#a78bfa;   // accent lighter (gradients)
$text:    #ffffff;
$sub:     rgba(255,255,255,.45);   // secondary text
$sub2:    rgba(255,255,255,.25);   // disabled / hint text

// Semantic
$success: #4ade80;
$error:   #f87171;
$warning: #fbbf24;
$info:    #60a5fa;
```

## Layout Rules

- **Page wrapper**: `background: $bg; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px;`
- **Card**: `background: $bg2; border: 1px solid $border; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; max-width: 480px;`
- **Inner block** (inside card): `background: $bg3; border: 1px solid $border; border-radius: 14px;`
- Mobile padding override (`max-width: 480px`): `padding: 28px 16px`

## Typography

- Headings: `font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.02em; color: $text`
- Page title: `font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 7vw, 2.4rem)`
- Card title: `font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 6vw, 2rem)`
- Labels (uppercase): `font-size: .82rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: $sub`
- Body: `color: $sub; font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.5`

## Buttons

Use the shared `Button` component variants:

| Variant | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `primary` | Main CTA — solid `$accent` background |
| `secondary` | Secondary action — `rgba(255,255,255,.08)` bg + border |
| `outline` | Tertiary — transparent + `$accent` border |
| `ghost` | Destructive / back / cancel — transparent, `$sub` text |

Never use colorful gradients (`#667eea → #764ba2`) for buttons — use `$accent` solid instead.

## Status Colors (badges, banners, dots)

```scss
// Success banner (e.g. resume game)
background: rgba(74,222,128,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.25);

// Error banner
background: rgba(248,113,113,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.2);

// Warning banner (e.g. opponent disconnected)
background: rgba(251,191,36,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,.2);

// Online dot
background: #4ade80; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(74,222,128,.5);

// Offline dot
background: #6b7280;
```

## Animations

- Entrances: `from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }` duration `.3s ease`
- Modal popup: `from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(.94); }` duration `.18s ease`
- Spinner: `border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); border-top-color: $accent;`
- Pulse: `0%,100% { opacity:1 } 50% { opacity:.5 }`

## Chess Board

Board square colors are **always kept as classic chess colors**:
```scss
.light { background-color: #f0d9b5; }
.dark  { background-color: #b58863; }
```
The board wrapper uses `background: $bg2; border: 1px solid $border; border-radius: 18px;`

## Icons

Always use **`lucide-react`** for UI icons — never emoji or Unicode symbols in interface elements.

```tsx
import { Bot, Flag, Handshake, LogOut, Zap, Target, Plus, List, Crown, ArrowLeft, X, RefreshCw, Clock, Check, Play, Swords, ClipboardList, User, Circle, BarChart2 } from "lucide-react";

// Usage inside buttons:
<Button variant="primary"><Target size={17} style={{ marginRight: 8 }} />Найти соперника</Button>

// Usage as standalone icon:
<Flag size={32} />
```

Exceptions: chess piece glyphs **on the board** (♙ ♟ ♖ etc.) are kept as Unicode — they're game content, not UI icons.

## Don'ts

- ❌ White/light cards: `background: white` or `rgba(255,255,255,.95)`
- ❌ Colorful page backgrounds: `linear-gradient(#667eea, #764ba2)` etc.
- ❌ Dark text on light bg: `color: #333`, `color: #666` on any surface
- ❌ Separate design tokens per page — keep tokens consistent
- ❌ Emoji in UI: 🎯📋🤖🎮⚡🏳️ — use lucide-react icons instead
